{"tid":605440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣ptt網友：香港租金貴過薪水　違反供求定律","createTime":"2018-03-25T16:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T05:45:47.000Z","uid":47714,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"84a0826e03b296156de5b7b9c1a7af7925a55d67","tid":605440,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336286580.A.444.html&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a030a69b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336286580.A.444.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 作者　chenglap (無想流流星拳)　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　 看板　historia<br />\n 時間　Sun May　6 14:42:58 2012<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n&rarr; innominate:這我不清楚,但租金漲過薪資的話,除非去搶銀行否則怎租?<br />\n&rarr; innominate:而一般的上班族薪資就那樣,你漲租金只是讓你房子沒錢收<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:所以可見台北房價高薪資低 逼房東要降租金配合薪資水準<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:香港就是寧可把屋空著也不會廉租給你.<br />\n&rarr; chenglap:簡單來說, 一個單位 300% 不降價, 好過三個單位 100%.<br />\n&rarr; innominate:香港這樣的情形很妙,也許有空再來研究一下<br />\n&rarr; innominate:理論上能賺一天是一天,因為你不廉租別人也會廉租<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fhistoria%2FM.1336482130.A.ED1.html&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c95fc862\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ptt.cc/bbs/historia/M.1336482130.A.ED1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 作者　dashanew (dasha)　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　看板　historia<br />\n 時間　Tue May　8 21:02:07 2012<br />\n───────────────────────────────────────<br />\n<br />\n推 obov:台北的房租/房價比　拿出去看真的是房租超便宜<br />\n&rarr; zeuklie:精確點來說是房租又比店租便宜非常多<br />\n推 Morisato:台北房子出租20年可能還沒回收一半,房租便宜到爆...<br />\n&rarr; kanako:台北市我有聽過房屋售價可以租同一間房子一百年的<br />\n&rarr; innominate:大台北地區的空房率很高,你不想租出去但別人想<br />\n推 bobju:呵呵,總有房市崩盤的一天,到時就會平衡租金比例. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fa3df80a9bf20649ff53fadca071811f6b3ddb","tid":605440,"uid":82777,"like":18,"dislike":181,"score":-163,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"香港租金係貴但點會高過人工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人人工低就以為人地一樣"},{"pid":"d2324225c54f8ea6af78a01400cca2f8837209c1","tid":605440,"uid":6845,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fa330cb327fd2942ff37cb5c602a999116ad70","tid":605440,"uid":6845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"21fa3df80a9bf20649ff53fadca071811f6b3ddb","tid":605440,"uid":82777,"like":18,"dislike":181,"score":-163,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"香港租金係貴但點會高過人工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人人工低就以為人地一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T16:28:08.000Z","msg":"太細既屋唔計掛 用台灣標準"},{"pid":"555bb400dad66d29cd282fe3c242911a3c0611dc","tid":605440,"uid":129924,"like":194,"dislike":3,"score":191,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:37:30.000Z","msg":"細間極既屋都租過萬一個月<br />\n但好大部份都係搵梗一萬幾千<br />\n今次人地又無講錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa38a219dd998dbbf2b7eb471126c9e2f3d6ba0","tid":605440,"uid":9231,"like":9,"dislike":46,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"台灣呢d鄉下地方生活係簡單d"},{"pid":"edc12198dfa97798a56e1ca5af5c496bc6d928c1","tid":605440,"uid":144774,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:40:37.000Z","msg":"所以咪有劏房"},{"pid":"896df79be27d1e316981c7bf824284b5d0bc8b3c","tid":605440,"uid":91982,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eda402e3c9ef9a310f39b60f1eee378ddf9fec8","tid":605440,"uid":27688,"like":4,"dislike":49,"score":-45,"quote":{"pid":"555bb400dad66d29cd282fe3c242911a3c0611dc","tid":605440,"uid":129924,"like":